  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to define the etiology of intra-abdominal infections, to study the
      role of Enterococcus spp and Pseudomonas aeruginosa in these infections and to clarify the
      need for specific enterococcal antimicrobial coverage.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
